aott/analysis/type_analysis/generic_specialization.runa
Generic Type Specialization Module for AOTT Performance

This module provides generic type specialization for the Runa AOTT system including:
- Generic instantiation tracking
- Specialization profitability analysis
- Monomorphization strategies
- Code duplication management
- Generic constraint solving
- Type parameter inference
- Specialization cache management
- Partial specialization support
- Generic interface specialization
- Cross-module specialization
- Template instantiation optimization
- Generic code size impact
- Runtime specialization decisions
- Speculative generic compilation
- Generic debugging support
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

